== Selenium-77, 78, 79, 80, 82 ==
{|
|{{Iso1|77|Se|R}}||{{Iso1|78|Se|R}}||{{Iso2|[[Se-79|79]]|Se|Y}}||{{Iso1|80|Se|R}}|| ||{{Iso1|82|Se|R}}
|}
Se-79, half-life of 327k years, is one of the [[long-lived fission products]].

